    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the captain of an arctic expedition. Months into the voyage, you discover an uncharted island, encased in a wall of ice. You decide to take a closer look and meet with your boat on the far side of the island. What will you discover? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unwind and relax as you explore colourful and atmospheric environments. No story, NPCs, cutscenes or distractions. Just you, exploring environments at your own pace. A super simple collectathon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing, peaceful, exploration-adventure full of enchanting detail </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for hidden items and special items, spread across all seven levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements to unlock! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring an original score by Emmy-nominated composer Nicholas Singer</p></li></ul>",
